##  1. `appsettings.json`

```json
"DataPurgeSettings": {
  "PurgeThresholdDays": 90,
  "Tables": [
    { "Name": "EventosSistema", "Enabled": true },
    { "Name": "ErroresApp", "Enabled": true },
    { "Name": "TransaccionesApi", "Enabled": true }
  ]
}
```

