## З 2. Configuraci贸n

```csharp
public class TableConfig
{
    public string Name { get; set; }
    public bool Enabled { get; set; }
}

public class DataPurgeSettings
{
    public int PurgeThresholdDays { get; set; }
    public List<TableConfig> Tables { get; set; }
}
```

